data.title: Lucky Kentucky Moonshine
data.text:
Introducing our newest family member Clear Shine, unlike the existing seven Lucky Kentucky Moonshine flavors, Clear Shine offers an honest “white whiskey” experience at a higher 88 proof. Are you feeling Lucky?

Visit a true grain to bottle distillery in downtown Louisville.
